{"tid":867510,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩野係你知，但唔知人地係咪都知","createTime":"2018-10-18T17:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T18:33:53.000Z","uid":177764,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0118b332467556925e9f0e8077ce4c597a35ef37","tid":867510,"uid":177764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T17:10:21.000Z","msg":"最近有學到原來資訊係有分 共有資訊 同 公共資訊<br />\n<br />\n共有資訊指既係大家都知道既野，但唔知道人地知唔知，例如你知道你細佬喺房打飛機，你老豆都知，但你地唔知對方知唔知，呢個就屬於共有資訊<br />\n<br />\n公共資訊指既就係大家都知道呢樣野，而人地都知你知<br />\n<br />\n有條仆街放左個無聲屁，我離佢最近，其他人有小小遠，好撚想知其他人知唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30debef4a189c7ba1d13bb2f4fc17524d30b7dd3","tid":867510,"uid":177764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T17:15:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9c824973759045a9a67c886d29ad40e8be7c65","tid":867510,"uid":177764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T17:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e88c392a434514bd5dc3fa23b4ffb350497d1e5","tid":867510,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T17:24:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7b1c27d7c8dae8987078a4a85ff486c2d4079fc","tid":867510,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T17:31:31.000Z","msg":"你邊到聽返黎？"},{"pid":"d133dd6c6971d533a8d017fa00c6ff412f0e617f","tid":867510,"uid":145923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T17:32:49.000Z","msg":"我屎眼有毛"},{"pid":"351c73d03d18a1b48a030fa8067aa9a345e4c34d","tid":867510,"uid":177764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e88c392a434514bd5dc3fa23b4ffb350497d1e5","tid":867510,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T17:24:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T18:32:11.000Z","msg":"人地知一早開你拖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/